Comment: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:52.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍貴的失物
Comment: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相識的你撿起
Comment: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交還給我
Comment: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說來　重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:20.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要寫上名字
Comment: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然會丟失於不知何處
Comment: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常被這樣告誡
Comment: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的錯
Comment: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不屬於任何人
