Comment: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨風　來吧手牽手
Comment: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,於空　配合對方步調
Comment: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,與你　沒錯　如果與你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯　正因為與你一起
